        <h3>3.3 Adding a Group</h3>
        <p>When the user clicks on <strong>"Add", a minimalist form appears:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Customer Group Name</strong>: Required (e.g., VIP Clients, Individuals, Businesses)</li>
            <li><strong>Price Calculation Type</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Calculation Percentage (%)</strong></li>
        </ul>
        <p>Once validated, the group is recorded and can be used in customer profiles.</p>
    </article>
